1. how to use 7zip utility under Linux?
 $ sudo apt-get install p7zip-full 
 $ 7z x ${file.7z}
ref: https://www.ibm.com/developerworks/community/blogs/6e6f6d1b-95c3-46df-8a26-b7efd8ee4b57/entry/how_to_use_7zip_on_linux_command_line144?lang=en 

2. how to create an user and add in sudo list?
 $ sudo adduser newme
 $ sudo usermod -aG sudo username
ref: https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-create-a-sudo-user-on-ubuntu-quickstart 

3. how to redirec to file while keep terminal output?
 $ {cmd} 2>&1 | tee file.txt
